WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:07.673 --> 00:00:13.573
remove under cowl and side fairing first

00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:24.000
I read manual while doing it

00:00:27.580 --> 00:00:28.740
need a 8mm hexagonalsocket

00:00:29.913 --> 00:00:31.913
a screwdriver

00:00:35.260 --> 00:00:39.280
a container for old coolant , new coolant

00:00:39.720 --> 00:00:42.160
remove the screw on the radiator cap

00:00:42.920 --> 00:00:51.920
remove radiator cap

00:00:54.480 --> 00:00:56.480
remove siphon hose

00:00:59.080 --> 00:01:01.840
release hose clamps

00:01:15.660 --> 00:01:17.660
remove resereve tank cover

00:01:23.280 --> 00:01:25.280
lower the siphon hose

00:01:32.360 --> 00:01:34.360
drain the water

00:01:37.980 --> 00:01:39.980
done

00:01:42.720 --> 00:01:55.640
add tap water to the reserve tank to clean it

00:01:56.200 --> 00:02:00.780
drain it out again

00:02:06.180 --> 00:02:08.180
8mm hex socket

00:02:12.520 --> 00:02:14.520
loosen the drain bolt

00:02:19.000 --> 00:02:28.520
draining

00:02:35.800 --> 00:02:37.800
install the siphon hose

00:02:50.020 --> 00:02:52.020
route the hose properly

00:02:53.220 --> 00:02:54.594
grease it just a little bie

00:02:55.814 --> 00:02:57.814
connect it to radiator

00:03:05.320 --> 00:03:07.320
snap the ring

00:03:13.280 --> 00:03:15.280
add new coolant

00:03:42.400 --> 00:03:44.400
till you see the water level up to the neck

00:03:48.440 --> 00:03:53.120
too heavy to hold by single hand,let me skip here

00:03:55.760 --> 00:04:00.500
after that, start the engine for 2~3 minutes

00:04:01.120 --> 00:04:07.900
coolant level gets lower after air is bleeded out
0:04:16.840,0:04:21.060
snap the throttle couple times

00:04:24.520 --> 00:04:26.520
fill up the coolant to the neck

00:04:27.260 --> 00:04:30.960
install radiator cap

00:04:49.720 --> 00:04:54.280
fasten the screw

00:05:03.400 --> 00:05:06.660
add coolant to the revserve tank

00:05:12.500 --> 00:05:16.180
and to the upper limit

00:05:18.820 --> 00:05:21.580
confirm it

00:05:28.627 --> 00:05:33.927
install reserve tank cover

00:05:40.740 --> 00:05:44.100
coolant replace completed

